### Admin API Test Requests
### Sử dụng với REST Client extension trong VS Code hoặc Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Login (để lấy token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@connectexe.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Get Dashboard Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Users List (với pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Users with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?page=0&size=10&searchQuery=john
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Users with Role Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?page=0&size=10&role=STUDENT
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Update User Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 7. Get Projects List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Projects with Status Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects?page=0&size=10&status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Projects with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects?page=0&size=10&searchQuery=smart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Approve Project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true,
  "reason": "Project meets all requirements"
}

### 11. Reject Project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": false,
  "reason": "Does not meet quality standards"
}

### 12. Get Recent Activities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/activities/recent?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Get More Activities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/activities/recent?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Delete Project
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
